summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2006 FLEETWOOD CHEYENNE.  WHILE THE VEHICLE WAS PARKED A GUST OF WIND BLEW THE BAG WHICH THE AWNING FOLDS INTO OFF OF THE SIDE OF THE VEHICLE.  UPON EXAMINING THE AWNING SHE NOTICED THE THREAD FOR THE BAG WAS VERY BRITTLE AND WAS EASILY SEPARATING.  THE VEHICLE WAS NOT TAKEN TO BE EXAMINED FOR THE CAUSE OF FAILURE AND HAS NOT BEEN REPAIRED.  THE VEHICLE DOES NOT RECORD MILEAGES.
